Rather, no.
“I thought I had made $1.6 billion for the bank and that from that simple fact, that would make them happy.”
Where did he get so much willpower to take that risk?
In my position I had to work gradually.
He joined Société Générale in 2000, exactly after finishing his studies in Lyon.
