If you win, we'll let you
"This is like a snowball," police said.
But it is said that the bosses knew all this or rather suspected it.
"While making money, they closed their eyes."
Only then came the blow earlier this year.
In one day he lost a billion euros.
After the weekend in mid-January he wanted to erase all traces.
When he arrived at work on Monday, he was no longer working at the bank.
